{"word":"προφητεύω","slug":"προφητεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προφητεύω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:προφήτης\">προφήτης</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘state or disclose divine will or purpose’, <b>prophesy <a href='B:470 7:22'>Mt 7:22</a>; <a href='B:510 2:17'>Ac 2:17f</a>; <a href='B:510 19:6'>19:6</a>; <a href='B:510 21:9'>21:9</a>; <a href='B:530 11:4'>1 Cor 11:4f</a>; <a href='B:530 13:9'>13:9</a>; <a href='B:530 14:1'>14:1</a>, <a href='B:530 14:3-5'>3-5</a>, <a href='B:530 14:24'>24</a>, <a href='B:530 14:31'>31</a>, <a href='B:530 14:39'>39</a>; <a href='B:730 11:3'>Rv 11:3</a>.</b> With focus on foretelling <b><a href='B:470 11:13'>Mt 11:13</a>; <a href='B:470 15:7'>15:7</a>; <a href='B:480 7:6'>Mk 7:6</a>; <a href='B:490 1:67'>Lk 1:67</a>; <a href='B:500 11:51'>J 11:51</a>; <a href='B:670 1:10'>1 Pt 1:10</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 14</a>; <a href='B:730 10:11'>Rv 10:11</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘disclose concealed information’, <b>prophesy,</b> in mockery, <el>π.</el> = reveal as a prophet would <b><a href='B:470 26:68'>Mt 26:68</a>; <a href='B:490 22:64'>Lk 22:64</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προφητεία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προφήτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}